summary: It's super shitty some replies people have been making about "respecting Taylor's privacy, and leave Taylor and Joe online."...
body: It’s super shitty some replies people have been making about “respecting Taylor’s privacy, and leave Taylor and Joe online.” Like, “she’s a celebrity, it comes with the territory, or she probably called them to have her pic taken.” WTF?!?! Yeah, you figured it out. Two people running away in fear, and it was preplanned. Taylor has nothing better to do than to have people following her wherever she goes in hopes of getting a good candid. That’s just sad y'all.
